headline: Here’s Why the Third Avenue Real Estate Value Fund Increased its Holdings in Prologis (PLD)
summary: Third Avenue Management, an investment management company based in New York City, released its “Third Avenue Real Estate Value Fund” second-quarter 2025 investor letter. A copy of the letter can be downloaded here. For the six months ended June 30, 2025, the fund returned +6.38% (after fees) compared to +6.66% (before fees) for the FTSE […]
